{
  "id": "adv_card_ngs_11_01",
  "title": "伊吹渚 1話 普通の子じゃなくて",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "私が『恋のタクト』にメインキャストとして出演！？\nあの大人気恋愛小説の実写ドラマ化ですよね！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Me‚ appearing as a main cast member in \"Tact of Love\"!?\nIt's the live-action drama of that super popular romance novel‚ right!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.693923219
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、その認識で間違いない\nそれにゴールデンタイムの二時間枠だぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ your understanding is correct.\nPlus‚ it's a two-hour Golden Time special.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "前の雑誌のインタビューで『恋のタクト』について熱く\n語っていただろう。それが先方の目に留まったみたいだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You spoke so passionately about \"Tact of Love\"\nin your last interview. Seems it caught their eye.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.7823582331
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それはなんだか恥ずかしいですね……\nあの時、結構我を忘れて語っていた気がするので……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "T-That's kind of embarrassing…\nI feel like I lost myself talking about it back then…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.3272552808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことはないさ\nそれに沙季からも面白い作品だって聞いたぞ\n心情描写が豊かな恋愛小説……なんだよな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not at all.\nBesides‚ Saki told me it's a great story too.\nA romance novel with rich emotional depth… right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.1474104882
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "はいっ！　お話自体は王道のラブストーリーなのに\n一つ一つの感情や情景の描写がほんっとうに素敵で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! The story itself is a classic romance‚\nbut the portrayal of emotions and scenery is truly wonderful…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.7266610783,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.5268648466
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "主人公のユイナは恋愛に興味なんてなかったんですけど\nある日、運命的な出会いをして価値観が変わるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yuina‚ the protagonist‚ had no interest in love‚\nbut a fated encounter changes her values one day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.3516253225,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "色褪せていた退屈な日常がどんどん彩り豊かになって\nただの空や毎日歩く道ですらキラキラと輝いて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Her dull‚ faded life starts to gain color‚\nand even the sky or the path she walks begins to sparkle…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.5933264734,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.1110823314
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "運命の人と一緒にいるだけで、何気ないものでも\nユイナにとって大切な宝物に変わっていくんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just being with her fated person turns ordinary things\ninto precious treasures for Yuina!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.2599931401,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "そして、そんな運命の相手と最後はゴールイン\n式を挙げた後は砂浜へ行って二人で鐘を鳴らして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And finally‚ she reaches the goal with her fated one.\nAfter the wedding‚ they go to the beach and ring the bell together…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.7266598067,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.5026692074
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "はっ、す、すみません……！\nつい熱が入り過ぎてしまいましたね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ s-sorry…!\nI got a bit too carried away unwittingly…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.2933264734,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "はは、本当に大好きなんだな。渚をメインキャストに\n選んだ先方の目に間違いはなかったな、俺も誇らしいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha‚ you really love it. Picking Nagisa as a main cast\nwas the right choice. I'm proud of you too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.8333312989,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.5226483983
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "そこまで言ってもらえるなんて……私も嬉しいです！\nでも、配役の詳細はまだ伝えられていないんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm so happy you said that… I'm glad too!\nBut haven't we been told the details of the casting yet?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.7753464701,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "先方から聞いた話だと\n初回の打ち合わせで配役の発表をするみたいだぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From what I heard from them‚\nit seems they'll announce the roles at the first meeting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.7666646322,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.0973436994
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、めずらしいですけど\nサプライズみたいで、なんだか楽しみですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ that's unusual‚\nbut it's like a surprise‚ I'm kind of looking forward to it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.8827836039,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.110926374
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、メインキャストといったら……まさか……\n主人公のユイナ役！？　私と髪型が似てるし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ if it's the main cast… could it be…\nThe protagonist Yuina!? Her hairstyle is similar to mine…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.3827836039,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "あ……もしかして親友のエマちゃん役かも！\nあの子もとっても素敵な立ち回りをする子なんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh… or maybe her best friend Emma!\nShe's a character with a truly wonderful role too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.5827836039,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.8537380221
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "実は、主人公以外の感情描写も丁寧に描かれてて！\n特に恋愛相談に乗る時のエマちゃんの言葉や仕草が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ the emotional portrayals of other characters are well-detailed!\nEspecially Emma's words and gestures during romance counseling…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.2827836039,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "はっ、また我を忘れてました……！\n『恋のタクト』の話になるとつい……えへへへへ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ I lost myself again…!\nWhenever we talk about \"Tact of Love‚\" I just… ehehehehe",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.7827836039,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 168.47335221
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "気にすることはないぞ\nそこまで思い入れが強いからこそ抜擢された訳だしな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't worry about it.\nThat passion is exactly why you were chosen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.4333312989,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "聞く必要はないかもしれないが、一応確認させてくれ\n出演する方向で今後のスケジュールを考えてもいいか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I probably don't need to ask‚ but let me check just in case.\nCan I plan the future schedule for you to appear?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.1666646322,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 182.819995785
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "はいっ！！　もちろんです！\nぜひ、ぜひお願いします！　ふふふっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes!! Of course!\nPlease‚ absolutely! Hehe",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.8482476555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 188.3697238924
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、どのキャラを演じられるんだろう～？\n登場人物全員素敵だからな～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ I wonder which character I'll be playing~?\nSince every character is so wonderful~…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.0333358765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01-ngs017.m4a",
      "text": "よーし、どの役を任されてもいいように\n今から原作を読み返して打ち合わせに備えますね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ to be ready for any role assigned‚\nI'll re-read the original work now to prepare for the meeting!",
        "id": ""
